5bci:<\/b> B\u0105d\u017a na bie\u017c\u0105co z nowymi funkcjami i zmianami, kt\u00f3re Amazon wprowadza, aby wspiera\u0107 sprzedawc\u00f3w. Zrozumienie tych zmian pozwoli Ci lepiej dostosowa\u0107 swoj\u0105 strategi\u0119 sprzeda\u017cy.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Podsumowuj\u0105c, zmiany w polityce Amazon mog\u0105 mie\u0107 znacz\u0105cy wp\u0142yw na Twoje dzia\u0142ania jako sprzedawcy. \u015aledzenie recenzji, dzielenie si\u0119 do\u015bwiadczeniami i korzystanie z nowych funkcji to kluczowe kroki, kt\u00f3re mog\u0105 zwi\u0119kszy\u0107 Twoje szanse na sukces.<\/p>\n<p><i>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/i><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h2>Czy wiesz, jak Amazon wspiera sprzedawc\u00f3w w walce z nieuczciwymi recenzjami?<\/h2>\n<p>W ostatnim <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":5342,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[5],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-5341","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-strategia"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5341"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=5341"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5341\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/5342"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=5341"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?po